==English==
===Noun===
'''[[spot]] [[check]]'''
#{{idiom}} A [[cursory]] [[inspection]] or [[examination]] or the inspection or examination of a [[sample]] of something.
#:''They do not measure each one, but they do a '''spot check''' on a few parts before shipping.''

===Verb===
'''spot check'''
#{{idiom}} To inspect or examine briefly, or by sampling.
#:''They '''spot check''' the rooms periodically for problems.''


===Alternative forms===
*[[spot-check]] is another common spelling for the verb, somewhat less commonly used for the noun.